    <title>试水的第一篇内容</title>
    <link href="zoutu.github.io/2020/04/23/%E8%AF%95%E6%B0%B4%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E7%AF%87%E5%86%85%E5%AE%B9/"/>
    <id>zoutu.github.io/2020/04/23/试水的第一篇内容/</id>
    <published>2020-04-23T03:07:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-04-23T12:58:33.510Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>用码云来建立博客有个弊端就是多出了一个目录 ，没错就是blog这个根目录。<br><br>和github、coding这些网站比较起来，就多了很多微调的步骤，比如调整搜索框的搜索功能。<br><br>对于hexo的兼容性并不是很好，因为很多路径都要改，也都不知道为什么要改<br></p><h3 id="路径会错乱，特别是使用别人的主题"><a href="#路径会错乱，特别是使用别人的主题" class="headerlink" title="路径会错乱，特别是使用别人的主题"></a>路径会错乱，特别是使用别人的主题</h3><p>原来是这样的代码，本地搭建后hexo s访问正常</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"header"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"image-logo"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"/"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"iconfont icon-search switchsearch"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"/search/"</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">"搜索"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"iconfont icon-menu switchmenu"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>但是在码云上就不行，因为多了blog路径，所以你得加上/blog 路径才正确。</p><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">"header"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"image-logo"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"/"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"iconfont icon-search switchsearch"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"/blog/search/"</span> <span class="attr">title</span>=<span class="string">"搜索"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">         <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">"iconfont icon-menu switchmenu"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">     <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"> <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>不然你点击了搜索框按钮后就会提示 Cannot /search 就贼烦的那种。<br>而且 不单是一处报错，很多的路径要改 ，最后百般无奈，还是来到了github搭建（真香！）。</p>]]></content>
    
    <summary type="html">
    
      
      
        &lt;p&gt;用码云来建立博客有个弊端就是多出了一个目录 ，没错就是blog这个根目录。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;和github、coding这些网站比较起来，就多了很多微调的步骤，比如调整搜索框的搜索功能。&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;对于hexo的兼容性并不是很好，因为很多路径都要改，也都不知道为什么要改&lt;
      
    
    </summary>
    
